  Worth Thinking Through:

  | Category           | Consideration                                              |
  |--------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|
  | Error Tracking     | Sentry? LogRocket? Or just console logs for MVP?           |
  | Analytics          | Plausible (privacy-first)? PostHog? Vercel Analytics?      |
  | Email              | Resend? SendGrid? (transactional emails, password resets)  |
  | Caching            | Redis? In-memory? Or rely on Vercel edge cache?            |
  | Background Jobs    | Inngest? Trigger.dev? Or SvelteKit server actions suffice? |
  | Search             | Postgres full-text? Meilisearch? Algolia?                  |
  | Real-time          | WebSockets? SSE? Or polling is enough?                     |
  | Rate Limiting      | Upstash? Built into Superforms?                            |
  | CI/CD              | GitHub Actions? Vercel auto-deploy?                        |
  | SEO                | svelte-meta-tags? Built-in head management?                |
  | Image Optimization | Vercel Image Optimization? Cloudflare Images?              |
  | Payments           | Stripe? LemonSqueezy? (if monetizing)                      |
  | Feature Flags      | PostHog? LaunchDarkly? Or simple env vars?                 |
